header.gameNote: SAN JUAN SHOOTOUT AT SAN JUAN PR

article.headline: Vanderbilt 75, Tennessee Tech 62
article.story: SAN JUAN, Puerto Rico (AP) -- Ted Skuchas scored 16 points to lead Vanderbilt to a 75-62 win Wednesday against Tennessee Tech in a San Juan Shootout semifinal. One of eight players to score in double figures, Skuchas was 7-for-9 from the field and added six rebounds for the Commodores. Alex Gordon added 15 points. Vanderbilt (8-3) outshot Tennessee Tech from the field, 42.9 percent to 39.2 percent. Belton Rivers led Tennessee Tech (5-5) with 14 points. Anthony Fisher added 13, and Amadi McKenzie had 11.
